{"id": "1221406462157262890", "channel_id": "1221406462157262890", "type": 0, "author_id": "1218510274747699211", "author_name": "yuzhe1", "author_bot": false, "content": "原先雷亚回血机制是当前血量的百分比×n＋自带的回血，现在的是每一次回血都重新计算百分比，如果是bug，为什么迟迟不在公告里写出，如果不是bug，在血肉池即将到来的时候做出暗改是否有点不合时宜？", "timestamp": "2024-03-24T10:33:13.213000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 15}, {"emoji": "🤡", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}], "attachments": [{"id": "1221406462702518445", "filename": "Screenrecording_20240324_182452.mp4", "content_type": "video/mp4", "size": 1984848, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1221406462157262890/1221406462702518445/Screenrecording_20240324_182452.mp4?ex=6a005ee9&is=69ff0d69&hm=e1223f26f6af35bf7ce087618b7a8042d8e58002c8f39274d109e25efd43abf3&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1221406462157262890", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "雷亚暗改为什么不发公告？", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1221607620734095470", "channel_id": "1221607620734095470", "type": 0, "author_id": "977903961694674974", "author_name": "navirecorbeau", "author_bot": false, "content": "rt，因為發現遊戲內公告和dc上修改過的公告有些不同，所以還會開嘛？\n\n另外就是原本的輪換規律是製劑➡️升格➡️金券➡️強效➡️深潛，但是現在是製劑➡️升格➡️製劑➡️強效➡️深潛➡️金券（？）", "timestamp": "2024-03-24T23:52:33.155000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1221607621405053009", "filename": "IMG_5224.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 824970, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1221607620734095470/1221607621405053009/IMG_5224.png?ex=6a007181&is=69ff2001&hm=b2ef4e664ce7c6f1733f26aadee8689c4a98a453b029e413f7e5c8712e2d5a04&"}, {"id": "1221607621908496556", "filename": "IMG_5221.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 867856, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1221607620734095470/1221607621908496556/IMG_5221.png?ex=6a007181&is=69ff2001&hm=86ec359a61ac8e10056d7c2eeeafaec2d70f28949fa457ed5904b8f3c3ef2c9a&"}, {"id": "1221607622378262608", "filename": "IMG_5222.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 872099, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1221607620734095470/1221607622378262608/IMG_5222.png?ex=6a007181&is=69ff2001&hm=c84049d1f7f26856406891d3018e0f23cd8a0872a962494263676aabce05ba28&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1221607620734095470", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「處理中」煉金美學還會開罵", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
{"id": "1221507806226677912", "channel_id": "1221507806226677912", "type": 0, "author_id": "723490875123957762", "author_name": "rafanetold_", "author_bot": false, "content": "建議將群星之酒的描述改成「下一張打出的指令卡額外生效一次」，減少誤解\n\n（原帖）\n\n如題，拿了群星之酒+和群星之酒，理論上應該觸發四次美的憐憫，卻只觸發了三次\n從下一張打出的指令卡生效兩次變成額外生效一次了，那麼是文案組還是程序員的鍋呢\n\n（全損畫質警告）", "timestamp": "2024-03-24T17:15:55.522000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-03-24T17:24:01.450000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1221507867677429790", "filename": "az_recorder_20240325_011051_edited.mp4", "content_type": "video/mp4", "size": 1879600, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1221507806226677912/1221507867677429790/az_recorder_20240325_011051_edited.mp4?ex=6a00bd5a&is=69ff6bda&hm=49e65cb6bbbd9ece12e6091e8f44b76bd9dcd0646b5214ce31ffd63a54e75f57&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1221507806226677912", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」（描述優化）群星之酒描述", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1221484189254160467", "channel_id": "1221484189254160467", "type": 0, "author_id": "733514425847513171", "author_name": "xuan4185", "author_bot": false, "content": "有兩段影片，第一段是被敵人打出死抗的同時加了力量但沒回血，第二段是手動觸發，有確實回血", "timestamp": "2024-03-24T15:42:04.797000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}], "attachments": [{"id": "1221484189908734053", "filename": "Screen_Recording_20240324_230539.mp4", "content_type": "video/mp4", "size": 2399509, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1221484189254160467/1221484189908734053/Screen_Recording_20240324_230539.mp4?ex=6a00a74c&is=69ff55cc&hm=81385bd9b7e60b01af09a7a24745619100fa130e64af648267aeb21c157f81d5&"}, {"id": "1221484190768304233", "filename": "Screen_Recording_20240324_230311.mp4", "content_type": "video/mp4", "size": 1871802, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1221484189254160467/1221484190768304233/Screen_Recording_20240324_230311.mp4?ex=6a00a74d&is=69ff55cd&hm=3f4cce700fd6f79483ebc6c1baa1e505f2b5ae1a9e71ec59ed1015a4e8cd8f30&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1221484189254160467", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「處理中」無上榮寵未正確觸發", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1221514725314265170", "channel_id": "1221514725314265170", "type": 0, "author_id": "1212339830835511347", "author_name": "muliupan", "author_bot": false, "content": "先讲图例，两颗胚胎，带脐带，蕾娅三启可以让大招加的力量翻倍。\n       图一写明可加17力量，且吞噬力量翻倍\n       图二开大，图三共获得了17x2+17共51点永久力量，第二胚胎未吃到翻倍效果。\n    这显然是不合理的，尤其是在把无限吞噬的一次性回血修复成按当前血量阶段回血之后。\n      因为这代表蕾娅大招现在是一颗胚胎一颗胚胎算的，而第二颗胚胎却吃不到三启效果。\n     明明第二颗胚胎能吃到当前血量0.o。\n还是说你文案里所谓的翻倍是翻倍但扣掉基础数值这样？这算什么翻倍。\n      哪怕在之前一次性回血的时候，无限吞的力量吃不到三启效果也是不合理的，更别说现在的阶段式生效。", "timestamp": "2024-03-24T17:43:25.161000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-03-24T23:10:42.210000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}, {"emoji": "😡", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1221514725477716039", "filename": "Screenshot_20240325_012636.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 20520, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1221514725314265170/1221514725477716039/Screenshot_20240325_012636.jpg?ex=6a00c3bd&is=69ff723d&hm=90aeb8decf2b2fdab75dd7c0e2680bc79c2540245df9d04ae514a4b5b17d4da4&"}, {"id": "1221514725704077382", "filename": "Screenshot_20240325_012621.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 31826, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1221514725314265170/1221514725704077382/Screenshot_20240325_012621.jpg?ex=6a00c3bd&is=69ff723d&hm=96c45ab8ce4cf0bb630f838760dbacedfa559c1b3a9e6aa7a3e09819742eeeea&"}, {"id": "1221514725939216544", "filename": "Screenshot_20240325_012656.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 38156, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1221514725314265170/1221514725939216544/Screenshot_20240325_012656.jpg?ex=6a00c3bd&is=69ff723d&hm=ed91b67e87f38387ea22f9af260e2ae11fd1dfe6cdc8e69aa0e0b30be28b99a2&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1221514725314265170", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」既然修了蕾娅大招回血bug，为什么不修无限吞噬少叠力量的bug？", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
