{"id": "1221465555467243550", "channel_id": "1221465555467243550", "type": 0, "author_id": "733514425847513171", "author_name": "xuan4185", "author_bot": false, "content": "雖然校貓應該不會那麼壞，但還是得避免直接修改公告內容，應該以重發的方式來進行公告調整，不然哪天又出現什麼“公告與內容不符”之類的問題，然後被部分人士認為是官方偷偷編輯公告進行削弱。\n而且重發也能讓大家注意到有新的訊息，直接對公告修改是不會跳通知的。", "timestamp": "2024-03-24T14:28:02.156000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1221465555467243550", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "我覺得，公告應該不能直接用編輯吧", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1221413039254016011", "channel_id": "1221413039254016011", "type": 0, "author_id": "969319742718509056", "author_name": "15828894371", "author_bot": false, "content": "不发公告，瞒着玩家削？以前的无限吞噬是按第一次百分比血量计算回血，现在变成了每次单独计算回血。回血量降低不少！希望给个合理解释。", "timestamp": "2024-03-24T10:59:21.315000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍🏻", "emoji_id": null, "count": 8}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1221413039254016011", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "（脐带）的雷亚狂气爆发被暗削了", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960", "1181168158678204497", "1181168183319736412"]}
{"id": "1221376614345216010", "channel_id": "1221376614345216010", "type": 0, "author_id": "1002938431271358494", "author_name": "1027vliaji", "author_bot": false, "content": "[狂气爆发]是不受到巨人之刃的暴击伤害加成，\n\n但是[吞噬]胚胎给的力量是可以给到[狂气爆发]上。\n明明都是显示是[狂气爆发]**后**和[吞噬]**后**，但是有些可以增加这次伤害，有些不可以。\n附视频，\n一段伤害为**40**，加吞噬胚胎的**17力量**，应该是**57**，但是触发了**血肉狂宴的力量加成**，所以变为62\n慢放可以看到buff跳出，分别是+5力量，34护盾和+17临时力量同时跳出，然后是回血，最后才是+5力量，所以推断为\n\n血肉狂宴的力量加成有两段，[吞噬]的5点力量可以增加到[狂气爆发]上，而原本的5点是结算之后的。", "timestamp": "2024-03-24T08:34:36.940000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-03-24T08:38:12.879000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1221376615783858186", "filename": "SB4A1J33C59O4.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1762202, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1221376614345216010/1221376615783858186/SB4A1J33C59O4.png?ex=6a00431d&is=69fef19d&hm=02157d0035ce6c3e9c14dd8e94ce2fdf3eb3594d3242453eb0c1e1879c612bbe&"}, {"id": "1221376616320471090", "filename": "MuMu12-20240324-160118.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1216533, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1221376614345216010/1221376616320471090/MuMu12-20240324-160118.png?ex=6a00431d&is=69fef19d&hm=6042672c5f9fcce1edbde7aa01a83c3ad2f6bb11da342b71174bcbbca2cba8cd&"}, {"id": "1221376616664666173", "filename": "S_3ISA5IC58Y058TC.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 161877, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1221376614345216010/1221376616664666173/S_3ISA5IC58Y058TC.png?ex=6a00431d&is=69fef19d&hm=6f476124e8e3048f1875b5a05b55f63d5f866acc4c1dae481642ecf995c79a4f&"}, {"id": "1221376617046343710", "filename": "QQ20240324161710.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 173150, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1221376614345216010/1221376617046343710/QQ20240324161710.png?ex=6a00431d&is=69fef19d&hm=d5ac05373bff43e6fb68f743a5c2e87154dad61f9a16b934f562fbec8fa88f00&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false,